data.description: This charming 1-1/2 story is located only a couple of blocks from historic downtown Chaska, Fireman's Park, restaurants & town festivities.  Easy access to multiple trails and shopping!  Home is nestled on a deep lot with a private, fenced backyard complete with a fire pit.  Home features an open floor plan with an office just off front entry.  New kitchen and dining flooring, a main floor laundry with oak floors and a full bath on the main with a 3/4 bath on upper level plus all 3 bedrooms are located on the second floor.  Full basement creates ample storage. Location, location, location....home has easy access to 169 and 212!
